{"tid":715460,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"🇫🇷巴黎討論帖","createTime":"2018-06-24T13:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T16:11:56.000Z","uid":89595,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0716b063712da25694414894fcc552ddc688e87b","tid":715460,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/france.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然巴黎嗰朵已經臭晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貴為歐洲最出名嘅首都之一<br />\n撇開啲scams唔講(多到可以另開一個帖討論)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實深入探究會發現除咗鐵塔玻璃塔象牙塔都仲有好多嘢可以發掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLa Terrasse des Galeries Lafayette<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/101600977/630/472/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F101600977%2F630%2F472%2Fimage.jpg&h=152b418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLes Deux Magots <br />\n名人caf&eacute;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nJean-Paul Sartre, Simone de Beauvoir, 卡繆，海明威都係嚟呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5143571bf03e1789200ba96834f118501228824e","tid":715460,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T15:14:10.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/france.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b798f819e09c0be72da887ba66cc40ce71137099","tid":715460,"uid":174905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T15:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/231725_638573b5b26bbbebe75494ba4a17366a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20