":715460,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:59:15.000Z","msg":"依家喺南法留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能又去巴黎9fing 下"},{"pid":"bdd4a37c4e8e2c0e8047e7deb3000394a53926ad","tid":715460,"uid":182994,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"521d4cbb45570f670d747f6fdd48be7ea077bddd","tid":715460,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8276c8b8d7618aece3dc73c84bfcbbe10fe48c3","tid":715460,"uid":182994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"雖然個個都話巴黎好危險 多難民好垃圾<br />\n但係呢個城市文化背景真係好深厚 其實幾值得去<br />\n呢兩年加埋去咗三次巴黎<br />\n幾乎次次去歐洲都要留幾日"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T18:48:57.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打中意去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"先利申:  我係絲 所以鍾意去既地方都可能偏港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你未必岩 不過都分享下<br />\n<br />\n去之前我都會search下有咩show或者exhibition 自己有睇過Yves saint laurent同Maison Margiela 都幾好睇<br />\n聽朋友講有個stand up comedy 叫 How to be a parisian in one hour好好笑 係諷刺巴黎人既 不過去果陣係opera個恐襲後幾日 所以都唔敢去 巴打有興趣可以google下 成日都有場<br />\n<br />\n行街就中意行瑪克區 多啲小眾牌子 另外果度有巴黎唯一一間nike lab啲波鞋同出面唔到 幾值得去<br />\n老佛爺幾乎唔會去 全部都係大陸人 有間百貨公司叫Le Bon Marche好多local行 都有好多香港人識既brand 主力係衫褲鞋 大brand既袋比較少 啲貨同老佛爺睇既好唔同 靚好多 啲sales又好有心機介紹岩你既衫 法國人啲taste唔錯 又唔hard sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n野食我都係跟人地網上啲介紹去 全部熱門旅遊餐廳都好垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而外國網啲推介有驚喜<br />\n有食幾間fine dining 有好有唔好 巴打有興趣我再講<br />\n平少少既話有間叫L&rsquo;Epi Dupin 我都想試 有香港人推介話正 你可以google下 好似唔錯<br />\n另外有間叫L&rsquo;avenue既小餐廳 係Champs elysees 好岩飲野 同埋成日有名人去 我上次去 Black Swan個編舞坐正我斜對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知巴打好唔好呢類型嘅野 我個人就幾鍾意 呢間野帶女去都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大路觀光野都去過大部份 我自己就好鍾意西堤島同聖路易島 好寧靜好舒服 最好就去呢兩個島即刻去瑪克區或者左岸 個對比好正<br />\n<br />\n另外博物館既話 個人覺得musee d'orsay正過羅浮宮好多 羅浮宮展品好似冇咩心思 反而呢間幾好 影相又靚 好似話係歐洲三大最靚博物館<br />\n<br />\n暫時淨係諗到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64591ec8b136309bfc2834c9f8bc0ffcd7037468","tid":715460,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:06:07.000Z","msg":"有乜撚野好負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  負評果個是咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cac6073d40539407d3f998966199376fa3f5d28","tid":715460,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64591ec8b136309bfc2834c9f8bc0ffcd7037468","tid":715460,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:06:07.000Z","msg":"有乜撚野好負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  負評果個是咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:08:06.000Z","msg":"正評返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總體嚟講我覺得巴黎其實好大<br />\n留個幾個禮拜慢慢細睇唔過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc1d61338185e3346e47b73c000411ecbb02b55","tid":715460,"uid":56483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"521d4cbb45570f670d747f6fdd48be7ea077bddd","tid":715460,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8276c8b8d7618aece3dc73c84bfcbbe10fe48c3","tid":715460,"uid":182994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"雖然個個都話巴黎好危險 多難民好垃圾<br />\n但係呢個城市文化背景真係好深厚 其實幾值得去<br />\n呢兩年加埋去咗三次巴黎<br />\n幾乎次次去歐洲都要留幾日"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T18:48:57.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打中意去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:35:25.000Z","msg":"我鍾意傷兵院，十點行到四點都未睇晒<br />\n<br />\n利申歷史撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9975208be53f7994b20e8891e5afe5a6b6c5c04","tid":715460,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"早排去左4日<br />\n落左2日半狗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得一日叫見到藍天<br />\n周圍去玩又要擔心俾人偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92038b4754b3bc0023a3a891b892109fa6e8d550","tid":715460,"uid":55233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"lm先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇緊機票可能過幾日去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf61d13a34e704426330328a60e59ab1774e5a18","tid":715460,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cac6073d40539407d3f998966199376fa3f5d28","tid":715460,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64591ec8b136309bfc2834c9f8bc0ffcd7037468","tid":715460,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:06:07.000Z","msg":"有乜撚野好負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  負評果個是咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:08:06.000Z","msg":"正評返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總體嚟講我覺得巴黎其實好大<br />\n留個幾個禮拜慢慢細睇唔過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T08:42:40.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以分享下有咩地方好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be447497a61fdea